plot: The Firm is a corporate reality TV game show in which 10 professionals demonstrate how they cope and perform in the business world. Hosted by renowned branding guru Peter Pek, and diamond retailer Chan Boon Yong, candidates who do not make the cut are eliminated each week. The show popularized the catchphrase &"You're terminated!&".   Written by  Kay Scott
